      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but wouldnt we be doing a disservice if we just ignore the other area? the instability there is mostly due to how things were set up during colonial times, and the people there actually need the help way more. if we only go where it's \"safe\" and \"predictable,\" aren't we just reinforcing the gap between the west and the rest of the world? wouldn't a rapid response team be more useful in a place that's actually struggling?",
